{"tid":2403350,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有旅行社業界倡當局協助港人到內地接種新冠疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-11T04:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T05:02:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"10c9ccc96687b2be51ee1c494641dd50c3454214","tid":2403350,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575280-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575280-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=eb45c919\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575280-20210211.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c1320bb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575280-20210211.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n有旅行社業界提出，政府協助港人到內地接種國內生產新型冠狀病毒疫苗，旅遊界會聯同跨境巴士公司負責提供「點對點」即日來回接載服務。有港區人大代表及政協委員表示支持，又促請政府盡快深入研究「疫苗護照」，以盡快通關通航。<br />\n<br />\n香港旅行社東主協會會長葉慶寧說，疫情導致本港經濟不景，旅遊業「零收入」，他擔心本港全民接種疫苗計劃仍需時，屆時本港商業會癱瘓，令失業率再上升，因此提出旅遊界及跨境巴士公司可以安排自願市民到內地接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n港區全國政協委員陳清霞亦憂慮，本港的疫苗接種計劃可能要數個月後落實，認為可參考安排港區人大和政協到深圳接種國藥疫苗的模式。"},{"pid":"f4fbba6f3ec1a27c7d30ebc65e061ba16d918a82","tid":2403350,"uid":321977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"送咗3萬thx上去打先啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bdea31285b84a5794fd1ea038287a7da7f6233e","tid":2403350,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"咁佢自己打撚咗未？"},{"pid":"a6d8f97421d8cf3a7cec6edea86ef2a4568f2021","tid":2403350,"uid":274772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"叫人上去送死<br />\n<br />\n都好  送多D藍絲上去"}]}